Description: Provides tools for analyzing and visualizing educational data,
    including the creation of charts, georeferenced maps, principal component
    analyses (PCA), and automatic generation of presentations. Features a
    comprehensive set of functions for conducting detailed analyses,
    generating standardized reports, and creating interactive visualizations
    to support evidence-based decision-making in the education sector.
